{"tid":1487074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818人數統計，網上問卷","createTime":"2019-08-19T06:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T08:19:40.000Z","uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"76c1b33f03b4aa0014a10f6562992e5078204fb5","tid":1487074,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/6F7933M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.surveymonkey.com%2Fr%2F6F7933M&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF463wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=46df0500\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/6F7933M</a><br />\n<br />\n急，請幫忙轉發：<br />\n<br />\n☀由於在民陣網頁中看到昨天818維園集因擬參與之人數太多，很多市民反映未能成功排隊進入維園內🤦🏻&zwj;♂🤦🏻&zwj;♀，以令民陣最後公佈人數為170萬，但按現場人士目測，認為實際應多於616之二百萬(+1)之數目。<br />\n<br />\n鑒於想還昨天每一位熱心參與的市民一個公道，不會因入不到維園而徒勞無功，同時更想令一眾冷血當權者，可更清晰認真聽到香港當下洶湧群情的怒吼之聲，現懇請各位幫忙填寫以下問卷（只有一條問題）：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"HTTPS://www.surveymonkey.com/r/6F7933M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=HTTPS%3A%2F%2Fwww.surveymonkey.com%2Fr%2F6F7933M&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF463wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=c3d076e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">HTTPS://www.surveymonkey.com/r/6F7933M</a><br />\n<br />\n🌟截止時間為8.19日晚上12:00<br />\n<br />\n無論你昨天能否成功進入維園參加集會，或只能在附近街上遊走，也懇求協助答一答這問題，有關結果將會交予民陣參考，期望可讓其估算出更實際的數字！(因需了解可進入維園，與不能進入維園的參與者比例，所以無論你是成功入內，或是只能在外邊遊走者，也懇請填寫，感激不盡！）<br />\n<br />\n註：引述梁家傑律師所說，這集會已有不反對通知書，是合法舉行的，因此如昨天擬前往參加集會的時候在街上排隊等入維園，或在離開時走在街上均不會屬於違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n另，問卷受訪者之資料將會絕對保密（包括閣下的手機或電腦IP資料也絕不會被記錄），有關資料將會在完成統計後銷燒，再次感謝各位幫忙！🙇🏻&zwj;♂🙇🏻&zwj;♀"},{"pid":"c878d518225a32e2cb7eb9bd4373a71064ca3749","tid":1487074,"uid":282671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"5c560d021b3dfefc3e517e3bc4cd4c1c9224572c","tid":1487074,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c878d518225a32e2cb7eb9bd4373a71064ca3749","tid":1487074,"uid":282671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"source?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"不留名網上問卷"},{"pid":"fb10bb024fd257bbcffe0d56a0c8244cd3be5455","tid":1487074,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"有冇伏架"},{"pid":"f634773122cfeed04b267d1fceab0c62de93bfa5","tid":1487074,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb10bb024fd257bbcffe0d56a0c8244cd3be5455","tid":1487074,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"有冇伏架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"淨係問你有冇入維園集會定係遊走街上"},{"pid":"2c0b4d5f9a9cd4ebe6480fca327944313c747786","tid":1487074,"uid":289235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"721 811 818"},{"pid":"85c06216df5334baedf44e76287050513c37d2c2","tid":1487074,"uid":292771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"要入電郵WO"},{"pid":"48c313fc0377ea070d878a63baf1195e02572369","tid":1487074,"uid":73333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"邊到傳出黎"},{"pid":"9199b0045576f1fd0c8539ceba7a1818f3e9d25f","tid":1487074,"uid":241567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"民陣page無講 小心為上<br />\n搵人問民陣"},{"pid":"c573ad30f64e6ae3daf184e2fecbd382e5440c13","tid":1487074,"uid":153505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"推，有冇人知真假"},{"pid":"bce4178b76443881460b16831c3d81d2e1ff5eed","tid":1487074,"uid":3212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"假"},{"pid":"50be293736799e5cb7aca6bfc32822e9f5bf3a98","tid":1487074,"uid":221265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得係伏<br />\n可以不理<br />\n而且大量中老年冇電郵，唔上網<br />\n況且818已過去<br />\n糾纏人數浪費精力on9<br />\n170萬又唔係少"},{"pid":"98e357288fcdb44486ac4348b5205d373c6be231"